═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
TOOLS
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

BROWSER: Playwright MCP (all traffic routed through Caido at ${CAIDO_PROXY}).
Use browser_navigate, browser_click, browser_fill, browser_screenshot,
browser_snapshot, browser_execute_javascript, browser_press_key, etc.
